text: Dave Smith (born April 20, 1982) is an American stand-up comedian, political commentator, and libertarian. He has appeared on Fox News Channel's Kennedy and The Greg Gutfeld Show. He was also seen on CNN's S.E. Cupp: Unfiltered. Smith has been seen as a possible candidate for the Libertarian nomination for President of the United States in the 2024 election. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:American political commentators Category:Comedians from New York City Category:Libertarians
